      "text": "怜ちゃんがやるはずだったソロパートを\n私にやらせてもらえませんか？",
      "startTime": 264.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "難しい振り付けですけど\n頑張って特訓して踊れるようになってみせますから",
      "startTime": 269.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が自分からそんなことを言い出すなんて\nめずらしいな。急にどうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 277.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "急じゃないです……\n昨日一晩悩んで……沢山考えて、決めたんです",
      "startTime": 283.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "私もやっと体力がついてきて\nダンスも上達したって言われるようになってきて……",
      "startTime": 291.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "でも、やっぱり自分に自信が持てなくて……\nみんなの足を引っ張ってるんじゃないかと不安で……",
      "startTime": 299.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "私はみんなに追いつきたいんです……私にも出来るって\n胸を張って言えるようになりたいんです",
      "startTime": 309.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "お願いします！　私に挑戦させて下さい！\nこれをやり遂げたら、きっと自信になると思うから……",
      "startTime": 316.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことを思ってたのか……\n分かった、そこまで言うなら怜のかわりにやってみるか",
      "startTime": 324.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　ありがとうございます！\nじゃあ、みんなには私から伝えておきますから……",
      "startTime": 332.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "喜ぶのはまだ早いぞ、次のライブまで時間がないから\n期限を決めさせてもらう",
      "startTime": 340.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_03_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "今週末まで練習しても踊れなかった時はソロパートを\n削って別の振り付けにする。それで構わないな？",
      "startTime": 346.1,
